packets.name: Regency Master Management Tokens
packets.author: regency
packets.description: This token is a master token for the Regency project in CryptoVoxels. It is intended as a wearable and used as a key to unlock content in Swag0x, Web3vm, CityWide, Bluefin, Airdrop, Underjaw and WorldLaw parcels. It attaches to super-powers within the Regency project including management operations.
